data.description: Wonderful opportunity in Pflugerville! Just 22 minutes from Austin. Less than seven minutes from IH 35. Great big lot that features a home with four bedroom, two full baths, two kitchens, and large garage that can be used for workshop. Home located at a dead end street, lots of privacy, very little traffic. Acreage offers a potential for expansion or much more. Come see today!
